arguments.template:
<sky-definition-list>
  <sky-definition-list-heading>
    Personal information
  </sky-definition-list-heading>
  <sky-definition-list-content
    *ngFor="let item of personalInfo">
    <sky-definition-list-label>
      {{item.label}}
    </sky-definition-list-label>
    <sky-definition-list-value>
      {{item.value}}
    </sky-definition-list-value>
  </sky-definition-list-content>
</sky-definition-list>
<sky-definition-list
  labelWidth="150px"
  defaultValue="No information found">
  <sky-definition-list-heading>
    System information
  </sky-definition-list-heading>
  <sky-definition-list-content
    *ngFor="let item of systemInfo">
    <sky-definition-list-label>
      {{item.label}}
    </sky-definition-list-label>
    <sky-definition-list-value>
      {{item.value}}
    </sky-definition-list-value>
  </sky-definition-list-content>
</sky-definition-list>
